snippet.title: YO-KAI WATCH Wibble Wobble | Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Jibanyan, Komasan, and other favorite Yo-kai have turned into wibbly wobbly, bite-sized Wib Wob! Level up individual Yo-kai, explore the world of Springdale, and defeat Yo-kai to befriend them.

A joint production between LEVEL-5 and NHN PlayArt, YO-KAI WATCH Wibble Wobble is an intense yet extremely cute mix of puzzle and RPG mechanics.
